					</div><!-- end .comment-meta -->

		<div class="comment-content">
			
			<p>I wonder who the first fool was to comply with this absurd notion that a &#8220;government&#8221; should grant itself the rights to control and oversee electronic frequencies. The FCC control over electronic airways was the very first NSA tracking and censorship program. The entire system was devised so they would know exactly who was talking about what and with who.</p>
