					</div><!-- end .comment-meta -->

		<div class="comment-content">
			
			<p>We should just let the oil, mining, and logging company coming in a strip mountains bare, etc etc. </p>
<p>RF is a natural resource, just like minerals, oil, and trees. They need to be regulated so that they are not abused and that all can enjoy them.</p>
