			<p>John Galt? ARRL exam?  Oh; that poor delusional John Galt. ;) Still lost on the ARRL exam though. Their exam consists of send us the yearly dues. And we will send you the membership journal every month. Maintain the VEC, keep an eye on Washington D.C.</p>
