					</div><!-- end .comment-meta -->

		<div class="comment-content">
			
			<p>I always thought they implemented time zones so that  didn&#8217;t have to deal with continent full of local times. We are the rail road 12 noon will be when we tell you it is.. Not that I could blame the rail roads.</p>
		</div><!-- end .comment-content -->

