					</div><!-- end .comment-meta -->

		<div class="comment-content">
			
			<p>@Me:<br />
That is an option as well. I&#8217;ve put on presentations a couple times, and even ran a build night once. (Tip: DO NOT do a build night with deadbug construction and expect the majority of the participants projects to work, even with instructions with pictures)</p>
