		<div class="reply">
			<a class='comment-reply-link' href='/2013/09/23/guest-rant-ham-radio-hackers-paradise/?replytocom=1063972#respond' onclick='return addComment.moveForm("comment-1063972", "1063972", "respond", "103405")'>Reply</a><span class="safe-comments-report-link">
