					</div><!-- end .comment-meta -->

		<div class="comment-content">
			
			<p>FWIW I&#8217;ve noticed that through my 20s and 30s a lot of social anxiety just goes away by itself. You just stop worrying about stuff so much. Try to relax, and think &#8220;what&#8217;s the worst that&#8217;s likely to happen?&#8221;.</p>
